summary: Replaces texture with a see through bikini texture
descriptionHtml:
Just place this in your data folder and it will replace the mesh files and texture files for the bikini and give you a see through chainmail texture.
Here is the original By ortog & Dimon99
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=10020

Required:
DIMONIZED UNP female body http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=6709
& http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=10020(install this first then this mod)
Install
Unpack archive to temporary location, copy/paste in game Data folder, overwrite.
Uninstall:
Delete folder:
Data/meshes/clothes/UNP bikini
Data/Textures/clothes/UNP bikini
Delete Data/UNPArmoredBikini.esp
author: Great Bizarro
